{"tid":1996658,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五一黃金周無內地團 旅行社受制限聚令未能辦本地遊","createTime":"2020-05-01T06:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T07:21:51.000Z","uid":166360,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a859c73fccca73da5d9dd6f8348e8bb67c2ab45","tid":1996658,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T06:09:14.000Z","msg":"五一黃金周無內地團 旅行社受制限聚令未能辦本地遊<br />\n2020-05-01 HKT 06:52<br />\n<br />\n受新型肺炎疫情影響，本港經歷自入境團登記制度以來，首個「零內地團」的五一黃金周。有旅行社嘗試推廣本地遊，彌補生意，但受制於限聚令，未能成團。<br />\n<br />\n酒店方面，價格較以往黃金周便宜。酒店訂房網站顯示，尖沙咀多間五星級酒店約一千多元一晚，旺角一間五星級酒店只需400多元；不少酒店推出住宿優惠套餐，吸引本地客。香港酒店業協會執行總幹事郭志傑表示，業界希望藉此彌補生意損失。他估計，疫情穩定後市道才有望好轉。被問到有沒有酒店面臨結業，他說政府推出保就業計劃等措施，有助業界繼續經營下去。<br />\n<br />\n零售店舖生意亦受旅客數目大減影響，記者到尖沙咀一帶了解過，有不少吉舖招租。有珠寶店員工預計，黃金周生意額只得兩成；有鐘錶行負責人說，業界已經出現倒閉潮；有藥房負責人表示，生意淡薄，形容是「等運到」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523702-20200501.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523702-20200501.htm&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=12999402\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523702-20200501.htm&h=e3213a50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523702-20200501.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">旅行社被限聚令攬炒了</span></span>"},{"pid":"24e50353fe46598b7334b45a78e8711ff9e4c3e5","tid":1996658,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"死曬咪冇"},{"pid":"09ac6790edd5a4c233e31eb58799cac50fbe26ad","tid":1996658,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:09:16.000Z","msg":"林鄭又考第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b0f0904cac4de937fefe1c6080febb358d1123","tid":1996658,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T07:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}